# Creator Collective Domain

Owns: creator/brand profiles, campaigns, reverse bids/proposals, messaging, deliverables, campaign payments, ratings.

## Invariants

- Closed/awarded campaigns reject new proposals
- Award/selection rules explicit (single-winner default unless PRD says otherwise)
- Payment/escrow release requires deliverable approval gates
- Brand/creator data isolation by ownership
- Ratings only after eligible completion states

## UI

Always `data-theme="creator"` (Playfair+Manrope, forest/terracotta). Never Soft Gift pink.
